			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>By <a href="http://www.alexdallymacfarlane.com/" target="_blank">Alex Dally MacFarlane</a></strong><br />
Read by: <a href="http://speakeasynarration.org/">Pamela Quevillon</a><br />
Originally published in <a href="http://daybreakmagazine.wordpress.com/">DayBreak Magazine</a><br />
