<li><em><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Who-Fears-Death-Nnedi-Okorafor/dp/075640617X/ref=sfwa-20">Who Fears Death</a></em><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Who-Fears-Death-Nnedi-Okorafor/dp/075640617X/ref=sfwa-20">, Nnedi Okorafor</a> (DAW)</li>
<li><em><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Blackout-Connie-Willis/dp/0345519833/">Blackout</a></em><em>/</em><em><a href="http://www.amazon.com/All-Clear-Connie-Willis/dp/0553807676/">All Clear</a></em>, Connie Willis (Spectra)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>The Ray Bradbury Award for Outstanding Dramatic Presentation </strong></p>
<ul>
<li><em>Despicable Me</em>, Pierre Coffin &amp; Chris Renaud  (directors), Ken Daurio &amp; Cinco Paul (screenplay), Sergio Pablos  (story) (Illumination Entertainment)</li>
