<li><em><a href="http://www.amazon.com/White-Curse-Workers-Holly-Black/dp/1416963979/">White Cat</a></em>, Holly Black (McElderry)</li>
<li><em><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Mockingjay-Final-Book-Hunger-Games/dp/0439023513/">Mockingjay</a></em>, Suzanne Collins (Scholastic Press; Scholastic UK)</li>
<li><em><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Hereville-How-Mirka-Got-Sword/dp/0810984229/">Hereville: How Mirka Got Her Sword</a></em>, Barry Deutsch (Amulet)</li>
