			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.blakecharlton.com/" target="_blank"><strong>By: Blake Charlton</strong></a><br />
Read by: Mur Lafferty<br />
Originally published in <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Seeds-Change-Tobias-S-Buckell/dp/0809573105/ref=sr_1_2?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1298046149&amp;sr=8-2" target="_blank">Seeds of Change</a><br />
