			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://felicityshoulders.com/" target="_blank"><strong>By: Felicity Shoulders</strong></a><br />
Read by: Mur Lafferty<br />
Originally published in <em><a href="http://www.asimovs.com/2011_03/index.shtml" target="_blank">Asimov&#8217;s</a>, Jan 2010 issue</em><br />
<a href="http://forum.escapeartists.net/index.php?board=1.0">Discuss on our forums.</a><br />
