		<title>Review: Monster Hunter International by Larry Correia</title>
		<link>http://escapepod.org/2011/01/16/review-monster-hunter-international-by-larry-correia/</link>
		<comments>http://escapepod.org/2011/01/16/review-monster-hunter-international-by-larry-correia/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 17 Jan 2011 00:57:26 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Sarah Frost</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Blog]]></category>
