		<link>http://escapepod.org/2010/12/18/review-the-habitation-of-the-blessed-by-catherynne-valente/</link>
		<comments>http://escapepod.org/2010/12/18/review-the-habitation-of-the-blessed-by-catherynne-valente/#comments</comments>
