			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong><a href="http://www.perytonpublishing.com/powtales.htm" target="_blank">By: Michael C. Lea</a></strong><br />
Read by: Jason Adams of <a href="http://www.indiesquidkid.com/">Indie Squid Kid</a><br />
First appeared in <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Book-Exodi-Michael-K-Eidson/dp/1936075008">The Book Of Exodi</a><br />
