			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong><a href="http://savetherobot.com/" target="_blank">By Chris Dahlen</a></strong><br />
Read by: <a href="http://www.arcanetimes.com/" target="_blank">Cheyenne Wright</a><br />
