		<title>Book Review: I Shall Wear Midnight, by Terry Pratchett</title>
		<link>http://escapepod.org/2010/10/22/book-review-i-shall-wear-midnight-by-terry-pratchett/</link>
		<comments>http://escapepod.org/2010/10/22/book-review-i-shall-wear-midnight-by-terry-pratchett/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Fri, 22 Oct 2010 09:59:43 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Josh Roseman</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Blog]]></category>
